values:
This just totally made my day!

There are two amazing <a href="http://darkarts-drabs.livejournal.com/7726.html">Draco drabbles</a> at <lj comm="darkarts_drabs">! There's the cutest ever kiddie!Draco and a delicious Death Eater!Draco! OMG I can't wait to hear who the writers are so that I can <s>worship at their feet</s> shower them with the praise they deserve! I had the hardest time deciding which one to vote for. Seriously, two of the best portrayals of Draco I've seen in ages! Three cheers for unredeemed!Draco! &hearts;

I really can't recommend enough that you go read them! <a href="http://darkarts-drabs.livejournal.com/7726.html">Go, go, go!</a>

My <lj comm="hp_beholder"> fic is FINALLY done! Yay! You wouldn't believe what a struggle it was. :)

<s>Now I'm kinda sorta asking if any of you lovely people would have time to take a quick look at it? It's due on Thursday, so I really do mean quick :) It's under 2K and very, very tame... Pretty please?</s>

Thank you! &hearts;
